Merc,<br><br>
Thanks for sharing your story about the Wall. It has many meanings for all of us. I, and all 'Nam Vets, really appreciate your Welcome Home. It has been a very long time &quot;away&quot; for many of us.<br><br>
I have been to the Wall twice, and I plan to go again next year, and the year after....<br><br>
The Traveling Wall is nearby this week, but I will be unable to visit it. It is not out of disrespect that I cannot visit it, but out of survival for some hard earned stability in my mind. By next year I will be ready to go to Washington, again.<br><br>
Merc, thanks again for your post. You are welcome to post here and participate, if you wish, at any time.<br><br>
My Best Regards,<br><br>
Art
